{"tid":2291350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"輝瑞藥廠：新冠疫苗有效率達百分之95","createTime":"2020-11-18T16:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T16:55:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5c2cb1a0a4520e2f31e486063e4b1f5de7e8eb","tid":2291350,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560702-20201118.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560702-20201118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5lznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=9bc8ae22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560702-20201118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6c406fcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560702-20201118.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國輝瑞藥廠發布與BioNTech合作研發的新型冠狀病毒疫苗的最後階段報告，顯示疫苗的有效率達到百分之95，並且未有出現嚴重副作用，另外，疫苗的有效率橫跨不同年齡及族裔，即使對65歲以上的人士，有效率亦能達到百分之94。<br />\n<br />\n輝瑞表示，計畫在數天內向美國食品及藥物管理局申請緊急授權使用。"},{"pid":"c7cc2696fd6ecd1a678d7629cc16d1294d82c523","tid":2291350,"uid":365136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"掂啦"},{"pid":"521cad7ca2fcac7debf036d7a846beecd4272ec2","tid":2291350,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717c92c324a81b529b1be76f82cbe5b5a444751a","tid":2291350,"uid":128514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"沒有新冠，只有武肺"}]}